'''斑尾鹃鸠'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Macropygia unchall''}}）为[[鸠鸽科|鸠鸽科]][[鹃鸠属|鹃鸠属]]的[[鸟类|鸟类]]。分布于自克什米尔地区、至印度、尼泊尔、不丹、孟加拉、缅甸、中南半岛、马来半岛、印度尼西亚以及[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]的华南一带北抵四川、[[福建|福建]]等地，主要生活于丘陵的树林中。该物种的模式产地在印度尼西亚爪哇。<ref name='id2051'/>

== 描述 ==
[[File:Barred_Cuckoo-dove.jpg|thumb]]
翅膀和尾巴是深褐色，身體的其他部位更接近棕褐色。雄性胸部有大量的橫斑條紋，且雌雄皆有淺綠色的頸背。 <ref name = HBWA2017 />體長{{Convert | 37 | to | 41 | cm | abbr = on}}，重{{Convert | 153 | to | 182 | g | abbr = on}}。[[虹膜|虹膜]]呈黃色或淺棕色，[[鳥喙|喙]]短，顏色為黑色，腳呈紅色。<ref name=Brazil2009>{{Cite book |chapter=Pigeons and Doves III |chapterurl=https://books.google.com/books?id=7-GgBoivL70C&pg=PA248&dq |last1=Brazil |first1=M. |title=Birds of East Asia. Eastern China, Taiwan, Korea, Japan and Eastern Russia |location=London |year=2009 |publisher=Christopher Helm |isbn=9780713670400 |page=248 |access-date=2020-07-21 |archive-date=2020-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727034644/https://books.google.com/books?id=7-GgBoivL70C&pg=PA248&dq |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=MacKinnon2000>{{Cite book |chapter=Barred Cuckoo Dove ''Macropygia unchall'' |chapterurl=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZaXi-P-heDQC&pg=PA133&dq |title=A Field Guide to the Birds of China |last=MacKinnon |first=J. R. |last2=Phillipps |first2=K. |last3=He |first3=F. |year=2000 |publisher=[[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]] |location=Oxford |isbn=9780198549406 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/fieldguidetobird00john/page/133 133] |url-access=registration |url=https://archive.org/details/fieldguidetobird00john/page/133 }}</ref>

與[[棕頭鵑鳩|棕頭鵑鳩]](little cuckoo-dove)外型相似，但是體型更大，更黑，並且在上背、胸部、兩翼覆蓋處和尾巴上有大量深色條紋。<ref name=Gibbs2010>{{Cite book |title=Pigeons and Doves: A Guide to the Pigeons and Doves of the World |last1=Gibbs |first1=D. |authorlink1=David Gibbs (naturalist)|year=2010 |publisher=A & C Black, [[Bloomsbury_Publishing|Bloomsbury Publishing]] |isbn=9781408135556 |location=London |page=}}</ref>

== 分佈和棲地 ==
斑尾鹃鸠分佈範圍從[[喜馬拉雅山|喜馬拉雅山]]到[[東南亞|東南亞]]。<ref name=MacKinnon2000/> 棲息地為海拔{{Convert|800|to|3000|m|abbr=on}}的山地斜坡，其上生長的亞熱帶濃密森林。<ref name=Brazil2009/><ref name=MacKinnon2000/> 此外更常出沒於舊林清除後的空地和邊緣，以及砍伐過次生林。<ref name=Gibbs2010/><ref name=Grewal2017>{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mzupDQAAQBAJ&pg=PA224 |page=224 |title=A Photographic Field Guide to the Birds of India, Pakistan, Nepal, Bhutan, Sri Lanka, and Bangladesh |first1=B. |last1=Grewal |first2=S. |last2=Sen |first3=S. |last3=Singh |first4=N. |last4=Devasar |first5=G. |last5=Bhatia |type=Paperback |year=2017 |location=Princeton, New Jersey |isbn=9780691176499 |publisher=[[Princeton_University_Press|Princeton University Press]] |access-date=2020-07-21 |archive-date=2020-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727013146/https://books.google.com/books?id=mzupDQAAQBAJ&pg=PA224 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==習性==
以一小群的方式活動及覓食。<ref name=Brazil2009/>生性害羞，接近時會迅速逃離，可以很快的速度在茂密的林木中飛行，在野外很難觀察到。在飛行中和地面上觀察到時，其尾巴都會顯得比斑鳩更長。

